quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,’Alif lām rọ̄. Ìwọ̀nyí ni àwọn āyah Tírà náà àti (àwọn āyah) al-Ƙur’ān t’ó ń yanjú ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá
  15,2,Ó ṣeé ṣe kí àwọn t’ó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nífẹ̀ẹ́ sí pé àwọn ìbá sì ti jẹ́ mùsùlùmí (nílé ayé)
  15,3,"Fi wọ́n sílẹ̀, kí wọ́n jẹ, kí wọ́n gbádùn, kí ìrètí (ẹ̀mí gígùn) kó àìrójú ráàyè bá wọn (láti ṣẹ̀sìn); láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀"
  15,4,A kò pa ìlú kan run rí àfi kí ó ní àkọsílẹ̀ tí A ti mọ̀
  15,5,Kò sí ìjọ kan (tí ó parun) ṣíwájú àkókò rẹ̀ (nínú Laohul-Mahfuuṭḥ); wọn kò sì níí sún un ṣíwájú fún wọn
  15,6,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ìwọ tí Wọ́n sọ al-Ƙur’ān kalẹ̀ fún, dájúdájú wèrè ni ẹ́"
  15,7,"Kí ni kò jẹ́ kí ìwọ mú àwọn mọlāika wá bá wa, tí ìwọ bá wà nínú àwọn olódodo?”"
  15,8,A ò níí sọ mọlāika kalẹ̀ bí kò ṣe pẹ̀lú òdodo. Wọn kò sì níí lọ́ wọn lára mọ́ nígbà náà (tí àwọn mọlāika bá sọ̀kalẹ̀)
  15,9,Dájúdájú Àwa l’A sọ Tírà Ìrántí kalẹ̀ (ìyẹn al-Ƙur’ān). Dájúdájú Àwa sì ni Olùṣọ́ rẹ̀
  15,10,"Dájúdájú ṣíwájú rẹ A ti rán (àwọn Òjíṣẹ́) níṣẹ́ sí àwọn ìjọ, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́"
  15,11,Òjíṣẹ́ kan kò sì níí dé bá wọn àfi kí wọ́n fi ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́
  15,12,Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń fi (àìsàn) sínú ọkàn àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀
  15,13,Wọn kò níí gba Ànábì (sollalāhu 'alayhi wa sallam) gbọ́; ìṣe (Allāhu lórí) àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́ kúkú ti ré kọjá
  15,14,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé A ṣí ìlẹ̀kùn kan sílẹ̀ fún wọn láti inú sánmọ̀, tí wọn kò sì yé gbabẹ̀ gùnkè lọ (sínú sánmọ̀)"
  15,15,"dájúdájú wọ́n á wí pé: “Wọ́n kúkú lo ìṣíjú fún wa ni. Ńṣe ni wọ́n ń dan wá.”"
  15,16,A kúkú fi àwọn ibùsọ̀ (ìràwọ̀) sínú sánmọ̀ (ayé). A sì ṣe é ní ọ̀ṣọ́ fún àwọn olùwòran
  15,17,"A sì fi ààbò bo ìmísí sánmọ̀ lọ́dọ̀ gbogbo èṣù, ẹni ẹ̀kọ̀"
  15,18,Àfi (èṣù) tí ó bá jí ọ̀rọ̀ gbọ́. Nígbà náà sì ni ògúnná pọ́nńbélé yó tẹ̀lé e láti ẹ̀yìn
  15,19,"Ilẹ̀, A tẹ́ ẹ pẹrẹsẹ. A sì ju àwọn àpáta t’ó dúró gbagidi sínú rẹ̀. A sì mú gbogbo n̄ǹkan tí ó ní òdíwọ̀n hù jáde láti inú rẹ̀"
  15,20,A ṣe ọ̀nà ìjẹ-ìmu sínú (ilé ayé) fun ẹ̀yin àti àwọn tí ẹ̀yin kò lè pèsè fún
  15,21,Kò sì sí kiní kan àfi kí ilé-ọrọ̀ rẹ̀ wà lọ́dọ̀ Wa. Àwa kò sì níí sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ àfi pẹ̀lú òdíwọ̀n tí A ti mọ̀
  15,22,"Àti pé A rán atẹ́gùn láti kó ẹ̀ṣújò jọ. A sì sọ omi kalẹ̀ láti sánmọ̀. Nítorí náà, A fun yín mu. Ẹ̀yin sì kọ́ ni ẹ kó omi òjò jọ (sójú sánmọ̀)"
  15,23,"Dájúdájú Àwa, Àwa mà l’À ń sọ (ẹ̀dá) di alààyè. A sì ń sọ ọ́ di òkú. Àwa sì ni A óò jogún (ẹ̀dá)"
  15,24,Àti pé dájúdájú A mọ àwọn olùgbawájú nínú yín. Dájúdájú A sì mọ àwọn olùgbẹ̀yìn
  15,25,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun l’Ó máa kó wọn jọ. Dájúdájú Òun ni Ọlọ́gbọ́n, Onímọ̀"
  15,26,"Dájúdájú A ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn láti ara amọ̀ t’ó ń dún koko, t’ó ti pàwọ̀dà"
  15,27,"Àti pé àlùjànnú, A ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ ṣíwájú (ènìyàn) láti ara iná alátẹ́gùn gbígbóná tí kò ní èéfín"
  15,28,"(Rántí) nígbà tí Olúwa rẹ sọ fún àwọn mọlāika pé: “Dájúdájú Èmi yóò ṣe ẹ̀dá abara kan láti ara amọ̀ t’ó ń dún koko, t’ó ti pàwọ̀dà"
  15,29,"Nígbà tí Mo bá ṣe é t’ó gún régé tán, tí Mo fẹ́ ẹ̀mí sí i (lára) nínú ẹ̀mí Mi (tí Mo dá), nígbà náà ẹ dojú bolẹ̀ fún un ní olùforíkanlẹ̀-kíni"
  15,30,"Nítorí náà, àwọn mọlāika, gbogbo wọn pátápátá sì forí kanlẹ̀ kí i"
  15,31,Àyàfi ’Iblīs. Ó kọ̀ láti wà nínú àwọn olùforíkanlẹ̀ náà
  15,32,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"’Iblīs, kí l’ó dí ọ lọ́wọ́ láti wà nínú àwọn olùforíkanlẹ̀"
  15,33,"Ó wí pé: \"Èmi kò níí forí kanlẹ̀ kí abara kan tí O ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ láti ara amọ̀ t’ó ń dún koko, t’ó ti pàwọ̀dà"
  15,34,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"Nítorí náà, jáde kúrò nínú rẹ̀. Dájúdájú, ìwọ ni ẹni-ẹ̀kọ̀"
  15,35,"Àti pé, dájúdájú ègún ń bẹ lórí rẹ títí di Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san"
  15,36,"Ó wí pé: “Olúwa mi, lọ́ mi lára títí di Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde.”"
  15,37,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú ìwọ wà lára àwọn tí A óò lọ́ lára"
  15,38,títí di ọjọ́ àkókò tí A ti mọ
  15,39,"Ó wí pé: \"Olúwa mi, fún wí pé O ti ṣe mí ní ẹni anù, dájúdájú emí yóò ṣe (aburú) ní ọ̀ṣọ́ fún wọn lórí ilẹ̀. Dájúdájú èmi yó sì kó gbogbo wọn sínú anù"
  15,40,"àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Rẹ, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà nínú wọn"
  15,41,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"(Ìdúróṣinṣin lójú) ọ̀nà tààrà, Ọwọ́ Mi ni èyí wà"
  15,42,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi, kò sí agbára kan fún ọ lórí wọn, àyàfi ẹni tí ó bá tẹ̀lé ọ nínú àwọn ẹni anù"
  15,43,Àti pé dájúdájú iná Jahanamọ ni àdéhùn fún gbogbo wọn
  15,44,Àwọn ojú ọ̀nà méje ń bẹ fún (iná). Àtúnpín tún wà fún ojú-ọ̀nà kọ̀ọ̀kan
  15,45,Dájúdájú àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu) máa wà nínú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra pẹ̀lú àwọn odò (t’ó ń ṣàn nísàlẹ̀ rẹ̀)
  15,46,"(A máa sọ pé): “Ẹ wọ inú rẹ̀ pẹ̀lú àlàáfíà ní olùfàyàbalẹ̀.”"
  15,47,"A sì máa yọ ohun tí ń bẹ nínú ọkàn wọn t’ó jẹ́ inúnibíni kúrò; (wọn yóò di) ọmọ-ìyá (ara wọn. Wọn yóò wà) lórí ibùsùn, tí wọn yóò kọjú síra wọn"
  15,48,Wàhálà kan kò níí bá wọn nínú rẹ̀. Wọn kò sì níí mú wọn jáde kúrò nínú rẹ̀
  15,49,"Fún àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi ní ìró pé dájúdájú Èmi ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  15,50,Àti pé dájúdájú ìyà Mi ni ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro
  15,51,Fún wọn ní ìró nípa àlejò (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm
  15,52,"(Rántí) nígbà tí wọ́n wọlé tọ̀ ọ́, wọ́n sì sọ pé: “Àlàáfíà”. Ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ẹ̀rù yín ń ba àwa.”"
  15,53,"Wọ́n sọ pé: \"Má ṣe bẹ̀rù. Dájúdájú àwa yóò fún ọ ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí) ọmọkùnrin onímímọ̀ kan"
  15,54,"Ó sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ̀ ń fún mi ní ìró ìdùnnú (nípa bíbí ọmọ) nígbà tí ogbó ti dé sí mi? Ìró ìdùnnú wo ni ẹ̀ ń fún mi ná"
  15,55,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “À ń fún ọ ní ìró ìdùnnú pẹ̀lú òdodo. Nítorí náà, má ṣe wà lára àwọn olùjákànmùná.”"
  15,56,"Ó sọ pé: “Kò mà sí ẹni tí ó máa jákànmùná nínú ìkẹ́ Olúwa Rẹ̀ bí kò ṣe àwọn olùṣìnà.”"
  15,57,"Ó sọ pé: “Kí tún ni ọ̀rọ̀ tí ẹ bá wá, ẹ̀yin Òjíṣẹ́?”"
  15,58,"Wọ́n sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú Wọ́n rán wa níṣẹ́ sí ìjọ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ ni"
  15,59,Àfi ará ilé (Ànábì) Lūt. Dájúdájú àwa yóò gba wọn là pátápátá
  15,60,Àfi ìyàwó rẹ̀; A ti kọ kádàrá rẹ̀ (pé) dájúdájú ó máa wà nínú àwọn t’ó máa ṣẹ́kù lẹ́yìn sínú ìparun
  15,61,Nígbà tí àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ dé ọ̀dọ̀ ará ilé (Ànábì) Lūt
  15,62,"(Ànábì Lūt) sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin jẹ́ àjòjì ènìyàn.”"
  15,63,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Rárá, a wá sọ́dọ̀ rẹ nítorí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣeyèméjì nípa rẹ̀"
  15,64,A mú òdodo wá bá ọ ni. Àti pé dájúdájú olódodo ni àwa
  15,65,"Nítorí náà, mú ará ilé rẹ jáde ní apá kan òru. Kí o sì tẹ̀lé wọn lẹ́yìn. Ẹnì kan nínú yín kò sì gbọdọ̀ ṣíjú wo ẹ̀yìn wò. Kí ẹ sì lọ sí àyè tí wọ́n ń pa láṣẹ fun yín"
  15,66,A sì jẹ́ kí ìdájọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ yìí hàn sí i pé dájúdájú A máa pa àwọn (ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀) wọ̀nyí run pátápátá nígbà tí wọ́n bá mọ́júmọ́
  15,67,"Àwọn ará ìlú náà dé, wọ́n sì ń yọ̀ sẹ̀sẹ̀"
  15,68,"(Ànábì Lūt) sọ pé: “Dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí ni àlejò mi. Nítorí náà, ẹ má ṣe dójú tì mí"
  15,69,Kí ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu. Kí ẹ sì má ṣe yẹpẹrẹ mi
  15,70,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ǹjẹ́ àwa kò ti kọ̀ fún ọ (nípa gbígba àlejò) àwọn ẹ̀dá?”"
  15,71,"Ó sọ pé: “Àwọn ọmọbìnrin mi nìwọ̀nyí, tí ẹ bá ní n̄ǹkan tí ẹ fẹ́ (fi wọ́n) ṣe.”"
  15,72,"(Allāhu sọ pé): “Mo fi ìṣẹ̀mí ìwọ (Ànábì Muhammad) búra; dájúdájú wọ́n kúkú wà nínú ìdààmú ọpọlọ, tí wọ́n ń pa rìdàrìdà.”"
  15,73,"Nítorí náà, ohùn igbe mú wọn nígbà tí òòrùn òwúrọ̀ yọ sí wọn"
  15,74,A sì sọ òkè ìlú wọn di ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀ (ìlú wọ́n dojú bolẹ̀). A tún rọ òjò òkúta amọ̀ (sísun) lé wọn lórí
  15,75,Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún àwọn alárìíwòye
  15,76,Dájúdájú (ìlú náà) kúkú wà lójú ọ̀nà (tí ẹ̀ ń tọ̀ lọ tọ̀ bọ̀)
  15,77,Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  15,78,Àwọn ará ’Aekah náà jẹ́ alábòsí
  15,79,A sì gbẹ́san lára wọn. Dájújájú àwọn ìlú méjèèjì l’ó kúkú wà lójú ọ̀nà gban̄gba (tí ẹ̀ ń tọ̀ lọ tọ̀ bọ̀)
  15,80,Dájúdájú àwọn ará Ihò àpáta pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́
  15,81,A sì fún wọn ní àwọn àmì Wa. Àmọ́ wọ́n gbúnrí kúrò níbẹ̀
  15,82,Wọ́n máa ń gbẹ́ àwọn ilé ìgbé ìfàyàbalẹ̀ sínú àwọn àpáta
  15,83,Ohùn igbe sì mú wọn nígbà tí wọ́n mọ́júmọ́
  15,84,Ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ kò sì rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀ (níbi ìyà)
  15,85,"A kò ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀, ilẹ̀ àti n̄ǹkan t’ó wà láààrin àwọn méjèèjì bí kò ṣe pẹ̀lú òdodo. Dájúdájú Àkókò náà máa dé. Nítorí náà, ṣàmójúkúrò ní àmójúkúrò t’ó rẹwà"
  15,86,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ ni Ẹlẹ́dàá, Onímọ̀"
  15,87,"Dájúdájú A fún ọ ní Sab‘u Mọthānī (ìyẹn, sūrah al-Fātihah) àti al-Ƙur’ān t’ó tóbi"
  15,88,Ìwọ kò gbọdọ̀ ṣíjú rẹ wo ohun tí A fi ṣe ìgbádún ayé lóríṣiríṣi fún àwọn kan nínú wọn. Má ṣe banújẹ́ nítorí wọn. Kí o sì rẹ apá rẹ nílẹ̀ fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  15,89,"Kí o sì sọ pé: “Dájúdájú èmi ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé.”"
  15,90,Gẹ́gẹ́ bí A ṣe sọ (ìyà) kalẹ̀ fún àwọn t’ó ń pín òdodo mọ́ irọ́
  15,91,àwọn tí wọ́n sọ al-Ƙur’ān di ìpínkúpìn-ín
  15,92,"Olúwa rẹ fi Ara Rẹ̀ búra fún ọ pé, A máa bi gbogbo wọn ní ìbéèrè"
  15,93,nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́
  15,94,"Nítorí náà, kéde n̄ǹkan tí A pa láṣẹ fún ọ. Kí o sì ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ"
  15,95,Dájúdájú Àwa yóò tó ọ (níbi aburú) àwọn oníyẹ̀yẹ́
  15,96,àwọn t’ó ń mú ọlọ́hun mìíràn mọ́ Allāhu. Láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀
  15,97,Àwa kúkú ti mọ̀ pé dájúdájú ohun tí wọ́n ń wí ń kó ìnira bá ọ
  15,98,"Nítorí náà, ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ìdúpẹ́ fún Olúwa rẹ. Kí o sì wà nínú àwọn olùforíkanlẹ̀ (fún Un)"
  15,99,"Jọ́sìn fún Olúwa rẹ títí àmọ̀dájú (ìyẹn, ikú) yóò fi dé bá ọ"